        <briefdescription>
<para>Save current settings to flash. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Computes CRC-16 of the current data. If it differs from the last known checksum, writes to flash and calls the change callback. If unchanged, this is a no-op (no flash write).</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>s</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Settings instance. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>SYN_OK on success, or flash write error. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
